
Zikula 1.2.8 (Forest) Release Credits
======================================

Zikula is, as with many successful open-source products, a huge
collaborative effort spanning many diverse talents from across the 
globe.  The list below gives an idea of some of the people that have 
helped in creating this release, and also those in other areas 
such as support and documentation.

Please note that this credits file only contains credits relevant to
this particular release.  For full credits, please refer 
to the file docs/previouscredits.txt. For credits of the many third party 
applications and tools used to build Zikula please refer to the file
docs/thirdpartycredits.txt


